# Tailwind CSS v4

CSS-first setup. Theme lives in `app/globals.css`.

## Do

- Import chain: `tailwindcss`, `tw-animate-css`, `shadcn/tailwind.css`.
- Use theme utilities: `bg-primary`, `text-primary-foreground`, `bg-background`, `text-foreground`, `text-muted-foreground`, `border-border`, `bg-sidebar`, `bg-card`.
- Dark mode via `.dark { ... }` and `@custom-variant dark` — not `tailwind.config`.
- Headings: `font-[family-name:var(--font-heading)]` where appropriate.

## Do not

- Create or edit `tailwind.config.ts` / `tailwind.config.js`.
- Hardcode one-off hex colors when a semantic token exists.
- Put business logic in CSS files.

## shadcn

- Add primitives with `bunx shadcn@latest add [component]`.
- New UI building blocks compose from `components/ui/*`.
